quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  63,4,"Mi ten twalav, a k taâoeb tiddi nnsen. Ma mmeslayen, tessemêasev i wawal nnsen. Amzun nitni d is$aôen i isenden, $ilen yal ti$ôi fellasen. Acengu, d nitni; êader iman ik segsen. A ten Ine$ Öebbi! Acêal wexxôen"
  63,5,"Ma nnan asen: \"yyaw, ad issuter Umazan n Öebbi a ppeppusemmêem\", ad bernen iqweôôa nnsen, a ten twaliv wexxôen s tem$weô"
  63,6,"Iâuva fellasen tessutrev, ne$ ur tessutrev ad ppusemmêen. Ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en"
  63,7,"Nitni i iqqaôen: \"ur pseddiqet, i wid iddan akked Umazan n Öebbi, alamma mmebruzzâen\". N Öebbi igerrujen igenwan akked tmurt, maca ixabiten ur mêiûen"
  63,8,"Qqaôen: \"ma nu$al ar Lmadina, war ccekk, uzmir ad issuffe$, segs, uôhif\". Tazmert, n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, maca, ixabiten ur éôin"
  63,9,"A wid iumnen! £uôwat a kwen ssbaâden, af usmekti n Öebbi, wayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen! Wid igan akka, ihi, widak d imexsuôen"
  63,10,"Ssedqet seg wayen i wen Nefka, uqbel a d tas tmeppant ar yiwen degwen, ad yini: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer ad iyi Teswexxôev ar lajel aqôib, ad seddqe$, ad ili$ seg wid imaânen"
  63,11,"Ur Irennu Öebbi di laâmeô, d awez$i, ma iusa d lajel is. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem"
  64,1,"I illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, sbuccuâen Öebbi. IneS tagelda; ineS wannuz; Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  64,2,"Neppa ikwen Ixelqen; segwen ajehli, segwen lmumen. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  64,3,"Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Imsel ikwen, Iûeggem amsal nnwen. £uôeS tu$alin"
  64,4,Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Iéôa ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren
  64,5,"Ma iusa kwen id usali n wid illan, zik, d ijehliyen? Jeôben lwexda n tikli nnsen. Fellasen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  64,6,"Ayagi, imi sen ppasen imazanen nnsen s ubeggen. Nnan: \"aâni d amdan ara $ inhun\"? D$a jehlen, xedâan. Ur Iclaâ Öebbi. Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz"
  64,7,"Pputebten ijehliyen ar, d awez$i, ur d pnekkaren. Ini: \"xaîi! S Mass iw, ard a d tekkrem, sinna ard a ppepwaxebbôem $ef wayen txeddmem\"! Ayagi, i Öebbi, d ushil"
  64,8,"Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked tafat id Nessers. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem"
  64,9,"Ass ideg ara kwen Issemlil, i wass ujemmel, ass nni, d ass um$uôôu. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, a t Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad iwekkeô i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  64,10,"Wid ijehlen u inekôen issekniyen nne£, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen. A taggara icemten"
  64,11,"Ur d teppas twa$it, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ad Inhu ul is. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci"
  64,12,"A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan! Ma twexxôem, i iwatan kan, i Umazan nne£, siwa anabi ipbegginen"
  64,13,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin"
  64,14,"A wid iumnen! S tidep, kra n tlawin nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d icenga nnwen. Ëadret iman nnwen segsen! Ma tsemmêem, teppum, tsemmêem, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  64,15,"Ayla nnwen akked dderya nnwen, d ahewwel kan, wanag, ar Öebbi, illa warraz ameqwôahan"
  64,16,"Ëezzbet i Öebbi ayen iwumi tzemrem. Ëesset, ôavit, seddqet! Yif it i iman nnwen. Wid ikksen ccêa i iman nnsen, widak d imerbaê"
  64,17,"Ma tôevlem i Öebbi aôeîîal igerzen, ad awen d Irr sin imuren, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Iceffu, Iêellem"
  64,18,"Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ivehôen, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"